value:
@ 2>/dev/null # 2>nul & echo off & goto BOF
:
if [ -z "$JAVA_HOME" ] ; then
  JAVACMD="java"
else
  JAVACMD="$JAVA_HOME/bin/java"
fi

exec "$JAVACMD"  $JAVA_OPTS -cp "$0" 'app.reader.server.Server' "$@"

exit

:BOF
setlocal
@echo off
setlocal EnableDelayedExpansion
set "JAVACMD=java.exe"
if not "%JAVA_HOME%"=="" set "JAVACMD=%JAVA_HOME%\bin\java.exe"

"%JAVACMD%"  %JAVA_OPTS% -cp "%~dpnx0" "app.reader.server.Server" %*

endlocal

endlocal
exit /B %errorlevel%
